title: Addition Tactics - Part 1: Left-to-right row addition for quicke
description:
Addition Tactics Part 1: Left-to-right addition for quicker sums, describes a technique for adding sets of consecutive and nonconsecutive numbers and obtaining estimates much more quickly and efficiently.
